<p class="MsoPlainText">Hi, <o:p></o:p></p>
<p class="MsoPlainText"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class="MsoPlainText">We are having problems with OpenMPI 1.6.3 &#8211; it gives the below error message when trying to run:<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class="MsoPlainText"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
